  <description><![CDATA[<p>The first thing you'll notice when you arrive at Hotel Mezdi is the incredible mountain views. When you're not busy skiing down the fantastic pistes nearby, you can sit back with a drink and soak up the mountains from the impressive floor-to-ceiling windows. The hotel's pretty close to being ski-in, ski-out - simply cross the road and you can ski straight to the lifts.</p>
<h2>Home away from home</h2>
<p>Once you arrive, you'll receive a warm welcome from the hotel team. The Rudiferia family have been welcoming guests to the hotel since 1952, and have transformed a quaint guesthouse into the modern four star hotel it is today. Make the most of the picturesque views of the <a data-udi="umb://document/47c7f0773b104efb87f3357e7314f393" href="/{localLink:umb://document/47c7f0773b104efb87f3357e7314f393}" title="The Dolomites Ski Area">Dolomites</a> from the comfort of your cosy hotel bedroom, each furnished in an attractive Alpine style. The lounge is the perfect spot to catch up with friends and family, and admire the stunning views of the Dolomiti mountains. Each day you can fuel up for a day of adventures at the varied breakfast buffet, and when you return tasty evening meals inspired by the region are served in the cosy restaurant.  The Mezdi is also ideal if you have little ones. It has large suites for families and a fun children's playroom with a ball-pool.</p>
<h2>Soothing spa</h2>
<p>The facilities just add to the great experience. The hotel has both an indoor and outdoor pool, relax with the waterfall and massage jets in the indoor pool or admire the panoramic views from the outdoor pool. When you need to soothe your ski legs, head to the wellness area with a range of saunas, steam baths and Kneipp - for the ultimate treat. f<span>acials, body treatments, massages, baths, and peels are available for a local fee. </span></p>
<h3>Exclusive to Inghams</h3>
<p>As a ski specialist tour operator we carefully select the very best accommodation in our resorts and package them with flights and transfers, so that you can make the most of your holiday. We have an exclusive agreement with Hotel Mezdi the only UK tour operator to package and sell holidays here - all the more reason to book with Inghams today!</p>]]></description>
